01:22:14,090 --> 01:22:15,970
O, hvala

695
01:22:22,670 --> 01:22:25,029
Koliko dugujete ovim momcima?

696
01:22:26,220 --> 01:22:28,810
Oko cetiri stotine

697
01:22:29,050 --> 01:22:30,760
Zasto moramo da mu damo?

698
01:22:31,760 --> 01:22:32,760
Zato sto mu dugujete

699
01:22:33,960 --> 01:22:35,960
Kao da nam treba jos jedna prodavnica
pica u kraju?!

700
01:22:37,720 --> 01:22:38,350
Ucuti!

701
01:22:42,119 --> 01:22:44,399
I? Sta se sada desava?

702
01:22:52,060 --> 01:22:53,270
Za Ordel

703
01:22:54,739 --> 01:23:02,739
Razmisljam o onome sto si rekla... kako
si govorila o svom bratu i statistici

704
01:23:03,750 --> 01:23:07,239
Oko 24 godine nosim tezak teret

705
01:23:08,020 --> 01:23:11,239
23 godine trazim nacina da ga se oslobodim

706
01:23:12,659 --> 01:23:16,500
Mislio sam da cu to postici na taj nacin
sto cu postati tebi znan

707
01:23:17,449 --> 01:23:21,449
govoreci ti ko sam bio i izvinjavajuci ti se

708
01:23:23,020 --> 01:23:25,619
Mastao sam da cu moci to da uradim

709
01:23:26,649 --> 01:23:31,710
Cineci mala dobra dela mislio sam da cu moci
da se iskupim za jedno lose koje sam ucinio

710
01:23:33,510 --> 01:23:40,760
Ali sam otkrio da, govoreci tebi o tome
ko sam ja u stvari, pomogao bih najvise samom sebi

711
01:23:42,520 --> 01:23:45,590
Ali sam isuvise slab da nosim taj teret

712
01:23:46,810 --> 01:23:50,350
I zelim da znas koliko mi je zao zbog svega

713
01:23:51,659 --> 01:23:55,279
Ja sam ubica i kukavica!

714
01:23:56,470 --> 01:24:00,210
I uvek ce me progoniti te dve stvari

715
01:24:14,050 --> 01:24:17,739
Procitao sam jednom neku knjigu

716
01:24:18,880 --> 01:24:24,739
Covek mora da predje cetiri etape
da bi se oslobodio osecaja krivice

717
01:24:23,640 --> 01:24:28,920
Prvi korak ukljucuje ono sto si uradio,
drugi ukljucuje

718
01:24:30,840 --> 01:24:36,500
Trece govori o odnosima sa komsijom,
ako mu ukrades pile, moras mu odneti drugo

719
01:24:38,739 --> 01:24:39,609
Tek onda si spreman za cetvrti korak

720
01:24:40,600 --> 01:24:41,640
Sto znaci da si spreman da se sretnes sa Bogom

721
01:24:44,350 --> 01:24:45,380
Treba da uradis istu stvar u istoj situaciji

722
01:24:45,380 --> 01:24:46,779
Samo neke stvari se ne mogu tako lako
vratiti kao ukradeno pileu to sam se
uverio pre 23 godine

723
01:24:51,800 --> 01:24:54,810
I ne verujem da ce tamo neki Bog
oprostiti ono sto sam uradio
ako se za to pokajem

724
01:24:58,180 --> 01:24:59,189
Onda idu treci i cetvrti korak

725
01:25:02,699 --> 01:25:09,840
a peti korak... vreme se pobrinulo da se
vise nikada ne vratimo na isto mesto
dva puta ma koliko to zeleli...

726
01:25:13,760 --> 01:25:17,439
Sto se mene tice, nikada necu biti
oslobodjen krivice

727
01:25:54,920 --> 01:25:57,050
Sta je sad bilo?!
Dosla maca na vratanca. A?!

728
01:25:59,479 --> 01:26:02,390
Edgarde, spusti pistolj dole

729
01:26:03,390 --> 01:26:04,390
Sta to radis?! Gubi se odavde!

730
01:26:08,390 --> 01:26:09,229
Ne budi glup!

731
01:26:10,229 --> 01:26:11,229
On je na mene pucao!

732
01:26:12,560 --> 01:26:13,470
On je na mene pucao!!!

733
01:26:14,090 --> 01:26:15,090
To sada nije bitno

734
01:26:16,619 --> 01:26:17,659
Jeste, bitno je!

735
01:26:18,029 --> 01:26:19,029
On j gotov, mrtav, vise ga nema!

736
01:26:20,029 --> 01:26:22,029
Nije vredan toga, veruj mi

737
01:26:26,079 --> 01:26:28,079
Sta to dodjavola radis?

738
01:26:29,079 --> 01:26:30,079
Edgard, spusti pistolj dole

739
01:26:35,529 --> 01:26:37,850
Nije me briga za njega!

740
01:26:40,239 --> 01:26:42,960
Ne, zajebi to!Odbij!

741
01:26:45,289 --> 01:26:46,829
Bezi od mene!Slusaj me!

742
01:26:47,829 --> 01:26:48,829
Slusaj me!

743
01:26:49,729 --> 01:26:51,989
Stani, ne, ne, ne

744
01:26:52,300 --> 01:26:53,300
Prestani, stani, NE

745
01:27:01,039 --> 01:27:03,800
Bezi, prestani, sta to radis?
Sklanjaj se sa mene!

746
01:27:07,699 --> 01:27:11,739
Pobegao je! Sranje!

747
01:27:13,869 --> 01:27:20,649
Sto si se umesao? Sta da je on upucao mene?
Dodjavola, koji je tvoj problem?

748
01:27:22,539 --> 01:27:24,909
Edgard...

749
01:27:32,149 --> 01:27:34,149
Sta dovraga...

750
01:27:42,560 --> 01:27:44,359
Sranje!

751
01:27:45,619 --> 01:27:46,619
Edgard!

752
01:27:47,250 --> 01:27:52,079
Edgard!Mama!

753
01:27:54,159 --> 01:27:56,850
Jesi li dobro? Jesi li dobro?
Dobro sam mama

754
01:28:01,170 --> 01:28:02,920
Izvini...

755
01:28:03,649 --> 01:28:04,649
Da nisi rekao ni rec

756
01:28:05,409 --> 01:28:10,020
Mama!

757
01:28:12,470 --> 01:28:15,560
Upomoc! Neka mi neko pomogne!

758
01:28:17,239 --> 01:28:20,119
Upomoc! Mama!!!

759
01:29:06,000 --> 01:29:07,739
Manjual?

760
01:29:08,310 --> 01:29:10,729
Manjual Dzordan?

761
01:29:18,699 --> 01:29:20,119
Koliko sam dugo ovde?

762
01:29:21,029 --> 01:29:22,029
Dva dana

763
01:29:48,750 --> 01:29:51,340
Ti si me spasla?

764
01:29:53,970 --> 01:29:54,970
I dovela ovde?

765
01:29:56,350 --> 01:30:00,770
Ne znam Manjuele, doktor kaze da
ces biti dobro

766
01:30:01,100 --> 01:30:08,329
Ovde imas nesto odece... nesto novca...

767
01:30:09,329 --> 01:30:10,329
Ne ostajem...

768
01:30:11,409 --> 01:30:17,010
Samo sam dosla da se uverim da si ok,
da nisam uzalud potrosila svoj trud i energiju

769
01:30:18,579 --> 01:30:19,579
...I znas sta?

770
01:30:20,310 --> 01:30:22,989
Htela sam da se orostim

771
01:30:25,949 --> 01:30:28,189
Mog li doci da te vidim?

772
01:30:29,189 --> 01:30:31,189
Nemoj molim te

773
01:30:35,439 --> 01:30:40,760
Molim te nikada nemoj vise da dodjes da me
vidis. Ovo je moj dom, moj grad...

774
01:30:42,239 --> 01:30:43,560
A ti imas ostatak sveta

775
01:31:24,789 --> 01:31:26,439
Ne mogu

776
01:31:27,569 --> 01:31:28,569
Kako mislis ne mozes?

777
01:31:30,970 --> 01:31:32,180
Moras

778
01:31:33,180 --> 01:31:35,180
Ova deca te vole, umes da ih nasmejes...

779
01:31:36,720 --> 01:31:38,199
Pa??

780
01:31:40,029 --> 01:31:42,529
Pa, ja mislim da je to vazno

781
01:31:43,920 --> 01:31:45,920
Da, ali ja nista ne znam

782
01:31:45,899 --> 01:31:48,310
Rutina...

783
01:31:51,039 --> 01:31:56,239
Samo prekini da zanovetas i uradi to,
razumece te oni

784
01:31:57,390 --> 01:31:58,350
Ne znam sta bi trebalo da radim

785
01:31:59,350 --> 01:32:00,350
Opusti se, smislices ti nesto...

786
01:32:01,500 --> 01:32:03,539
Ok?

787
01:32:07,840 --> 01:32:09,479
Dobro dosao nazad

788
01:32:15,329 --> 01:32:17,229
Bices ti ok

789
01:33:43,020 --> 01:33:45,329
...to je 15$

790
01:33:46,680 --> 01:33:49,310
15$?

791
01:33:50,840 --> 01:33:52,840
Parking je besplatan...

792
01:33:54,170 --> 01:33:55,170
Hvala vam!

